{"id":283522,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/【组图】网民恶搞回应浙江死猪事件：少年pig的奇/","date":"2013-03-12T06:29:47Z","modified":"2017-05-02T07:03:07Z","title":"【图说天朝】浙江死猪事件：少年Pig的奇幻漂流","content":"<p>近日，黄浦江上出现的大量死猪让许多民众感到不安。然而针对这一事件，上海市农委和浙江省农业厅却分别给出了完全不同的解释。前者称从死猪样本中检出猪圆环病毒病，是一种不会人畜共患的传染性疾病；而后者则称死猪多为冻死，浙江目前没有猪瘟。</p>\n<p>然而，大部分民众认为浙江省农业厅给出的“冻死猪”说法并不可信；不少人将这则事件戏称为“少年Pig的奇幻漂流”，更有一些网民以此为主题创作了漫画和PS图片：</p>\n<p>（相关阅读：<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/%E6%B5%99%E6%B1%9F%E6%AD%BB%E7%8C%AA%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6/\">浙江死猪事件</a>）</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_283527\" style=\"width: 450px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/767e4963tw1e2msnltqlbj.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-283527\" alt=\"767e4963tw1e2msnltqlbj\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/767e4963tw1e2msnltqlbj.jpg\" width=\"440\" height=\"247\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/767e4963tw1e2msnltqlbj.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/767e4963tw1e2msnltqlbj-300x168.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">作者：新浪微博 @大尸凶的漫画</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_283590\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/蟹农场漫画：一江代表向东流.gif\"><img class=\" wp-image-283590\" alt=\"蟹农场漫画：一江代表向东流\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/蟹农场漫画：一江代表向东流.gif\" width=\"450\" height=\"320\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">@蟹农场漫画：一江代表向东流。</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">\n<div id=\"attachment_283523\" style=\"width: 450px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/6aa09e8fgw1e2mqxmuqryj.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-283523\" alt=\"6aa09e8fgw1e2mqxmuqryj\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/6aa09e8fgw1e2mqxmuqryj.jpg\" width=\"440\" height=\"337\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/6aa09e8fgw1e2mqxmuqryj.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/6aa09e8fgw1e2mqxmuqryj-300x229.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">作者：新浪微博@谷大白话</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_283595\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/大尸凶的漫画：免费喝汤.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-283595\" alt=\"大尸凶的漫画：免费喝汤\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/大尸凶的漫画：免费喝汤.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"580\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/大尸凶的漫画：免费喝汤.jpg 700w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/大尸凶的漫画：免费喝汤-232x300.jpg 232w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">@大尸凶的漫画：魔都人民喝免费“肉汤”很淡定。</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_283599\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/梦晨伤：一面镜子.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-283599 \" alt=\"梦晨伤：一面镜子\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/梦晨伤：一面镜子.jpg\" width=\"450\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/梦晨伤：一面镜子.jpg 512w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/梦晨伤：一面镜子-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/梦晨伤：一面镜子-300x300.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/梦晨伤：一面镜子-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">@梦晨伤：【偶感】黄浦江是一面中国人的镜子。</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_283600\" style=\"width: 450px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/6463577djw1e2mp623pvrj.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-283600\" alt=\"6463577djw1e2mp623pvrj\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/6463577djw1e2mp623pvrj.jpg\" width=\"440\" height=\"293\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/6463577djw1e2mp623pvrj.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/6463577djw1e2mp623pvrj-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">@记者刘向南：万头死猪入江，终于培育出了新品种：黄浦江鱼。</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">\n<div id=\"attachment_283597\" style=\"width: 464px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/勾犇漫画：别冻着.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-283597\" alt=\"勾犇漫画：别冻着\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/勾犇漫画：别冻着.jpg\" width=\"454\" height=\"635\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/勾犇漫画：别冻着.jpg 454w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/勾犇漫画：别冻着-214x300.jpg 214w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 454px) 100vw, 454px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">@勾犇漫画：嘉兴几万头猪死因调查：1.不满饲料添加抗生素，集体跳下黄浦江自杀；2.养殖场水污染严重到黄浦江取喝水，不小心淹死的；3.惊闻铁道部殁了，伤心殉葬；4.身在雾霾自强不吸，憋死了；PS：浙江省农业厅：黄浦江死猪多系冻死。</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">\n<div id=\"attachment_283524\" style=\"width: 450px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/9f5ecc51jw1e2mwwtpb74j.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-283524\" alt=\"9f5ecc51jw1e2mwwtpb74j\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/9f5ecc51jw1e2mwwtpb74j.jpg\" width=\"440\" height=\"582\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/9f5ecc51jw1e2mwwtpb74j.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/9f5ecc51jw1e2mwwtpb74j-226x300.jpg 226w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">作者：新浪微博 @星星同学v</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_283561\" style=\"width: 450px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/7c523089tw1e2mtpxl1opj.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-283561\" alt=\"7c523089tw1e2mtpxl1opj\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/7c523089tw1e2mtpxl1opj.jpg\" width=\"440\" height=\"624\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/7c523089tw1e2mtpxl1opj.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/7c523089tw1e2mtpxl1opj-211x300.jpg 211w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">作者：新浪微博 @穿越-时光</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_283525\" style=\"width: 450px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/56e24c02jw1e2mrxfu5mlj.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-283525\" alt=\"56e24c02jw1e2mrxfu5mlj\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/56e24c02jw1e2mrxfu5mlj.jpg\" width=\"440\" height=\"691\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/56e24c02jw1e2mrxfu5mlj.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/56e24c02jw1e2mrxfu5mlj-191x300.jpg 191w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">作者：新浪微博 @勾犇漫画</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">另附两则官方新闻截图：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/死猪辟谣.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-283556 aligncenter\" alt=\"死猪辟谣\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/死猪辟谣.jpg\" width=\"440\" height=\"442\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/死猪辟谣.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/死猪辟谣-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/死猪辟谣-298x300.jpg 298w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/死猪辟谣-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,17016,21627,20532,13789],"tags":[9129,28578,13419,9250,17389,22714,22606]}